mindmap
  root((HTTP Lifecycle))
    User_Initiation
      Browser_Action
        :::connection
        Translates URL to IP via DNS
      Request_Construction
        :::connection
        Packages Headers and Method
    
    Connection_Layer
      TCP_Handshake
        :::connection
        Establishes "Three-Way" reliability
      TLS_Encryption
        :::connection
        Secures data via HTTPS certificate
    
    The_Transmission
      Request_Sent
        :::connection
        Binary data travels over network
      Server_Reception
        :::connection
        Web server parses the incoming "stream"
    
    Server_Logic
      Resource_Lookup
        :::connection
        Checks disk or Database for file
      Response_Generation
        :::connection
        Attaches Status Code (e.g., 200 OK)
    
    The_Return
      Data_Transfer
        :::connection
        Sends HTML/CSS/JS chunks back
      Browser_Rendering
        :::connection
        Interprets code to draw the UI